posts.title: Man Utd
posts.body:
Manchester United Football Club is an English football club based in the Trafford district of the city of Manchester . Founded in 1878 as Newton Heath , Manchester United plays at Old Trafford , its historic stadium, which derives its nickname "Theatre of Dreams" from the exploits achieved over the years by the Mancunian club.
